{"tid":2487604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呃錢FaceBook網購 Japan Toy日本代購","createTime":"2021-04-13T15:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T06:14:13.000Z","uid":237728,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"500a498b39690f1949ae258e89bb08ee5d23d5a6","tid":2487604,"uid":237728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"事源早幾日，見到呢個網賣Marvel精品（Avenger啤牌）<br />\n咁我見幾靚，又有朋友一齊有趣，就一次過訂三件<br />\n點知：<br />\n佢原本唔俾我比半訂<br />\n我就諗住少少錢$300，咁我就唔同佢計較一次過俾晒<br />\n<br />\n點知比完錢<br />\n我隔幾個鐘問佢我可唔可以訂多兩副<br />\n有朋友有興趣<br />\n佢唔覆<br />\n<br />\n然後問佢幾時寄幾時有貨又唔覆<br />\n然後喺留言問佢佢又限制我留言功能<br />\n而家我俾咗錢貨又收唔到，人都冇影<br />\n<br />\n最仆街係我叫朋友幫我打探下<br />\n然後佢見到我朋友話買即刻就秒回我幾個朋友<br />\n但係就唔覆我<br />\n而家仲要封鎖埋我<br />\n<br />\n大家真係小心，屌，仆街<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Japan-Toys-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BB%A3%E8%B3%BC-108282714069936/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJapan-Toys-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25B3%25BC-108282714069936%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11HhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=7696917b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Japan-Toys-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BB%A3%E8%B3%BC-108282714069936/</a>"},{"pid":"31baf7ae56446f61297dc8cbce8153ca18244e4e","tid":2487604,"uid":121233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:07:09.000Z","msg":"點解依家仲有咁多on9中招<br />\n屌你 醒少少搵間有實體鋪嘅買野啦"},{"pid":"9a833a03a81c186d0ad741c3bc3b4b75949e693b","tid":2487604,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/a70/d96/a70d960e8621e1bad2d4cfd34db47a8fbe248e26_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fa70%2Fd96%2Fa70d960e8621e1bad2d4cfd34db47a8fbe248e26_n.jpg&h=4590078c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef4ed92eaffcd188f5a46e3ee6aaa0d8c38deaff","tid":2487604,"uid":70704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply